# Supplier Evaluation System (World Cup Scale)

A standardized, high-stakes supplier evaluation framework designed for massive-scale projects (e.g., World Cup prediction games with 10M+ users).

**This project is designed to be used with an AI Agent.** You provide the context (transcripts, docs), and the Agent structures the evaluation.

